title: SECRET TIBETAN MENTALPHYSICS TEACHINGS - EDWIN DINGLE - PART 2
description:
SECRET TIBETAN MENTALPHYSICS TEACHINGS - EDWIN DINGLE - PART 2

Part Two of this collection contains over 22 hours of Mentalphysics teaching lessons narrated by its founder Edwin John Dingle, also known by his religious name Ding Le Mei. These exceedingly rare recordings are now available for the first time in MP3 audio format.

Mentalphysics was a course of Tibetan teachings on pranayama breathing exercises, meditation, and more, brought to the west in the early-mid twentienth century by Edwin John Dingle, an explorer who studied eastern esoteric teachings for several years in Singapore and Tibet. 

Be sure and search for the additional parts to this extremely rare collection of materials, and please do everything you can to help share them with others.
